<lb n="0884c20" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0884c21" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1367</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0884c22" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0884011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本</note>佛說大普賢陀羅尼<note n="0884012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">經＋（出廣濟眾生經第四卷中）夾註【元】</note><app n="0884012"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">經<note place="inline">出廣濟眾生經第四卷中</note></rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0884c23" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0884c24" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0884013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（舊）＋失【元】【明】</note><app n="0884013"><lem wit="【大】">失</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">舊失</rdg></app>譯<note n="0884014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔人名今附梁錄〕－【宋】，人名今＝師名開元【元】【明】</note><app n="0884014"><lem wit="【大】">人名今附梁錄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">&lac;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">師名開元附梁錄</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0884c25" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0884c2501">如是我聞。一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。
<lb n="0884c26" ed="T"/>時佛告阿難。吾今說大普賢&CB00057;。汝當受持。</p>
<lb n="0884c27" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0884c2701" type="dharani">多擲多　阿&CB00062;　那&CB00062;　<note n="0884015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">茶＝荼【三】＊</note><note n="0884015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">茶＝荼【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0884015"><lem wit="【大】">茶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">荼</rdg></app>彌<app source="0884015" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">茶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">荼</rdg></app>　遮居梨
<lb n="0884c28" ed="T"/>　居梨<app source="0884015" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">茶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">荼</rdg></app>也　居梨<app source="0884015" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">茶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">荼</rdg></app>也拔坻　思提　思
<lb n="0884c29" ed="T"/>陀　婆夢坻</p><p id="pT21p0884c2905" place="inline">阿難此大普賢&CB00057;。遮滅一切
<pb n="0885a" id="T21.1367.0885a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0885a01" ed="T"/>兵刃。除一切怨<note n="0885001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">仇＋（諸怨）【三】</note><note n="0885001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">仇＋（諸怨）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0885001"><lem wit="【大】">仇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">仇諸怨</rdg></app>。除一切夜叉羅剎復多等
<lb n="0885a02" ed="T"/>畏。除一切不得食下鬼名。</p>
<lb n="0885a03" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0885a0301">胡摩兜<note place="inline">一</note>烏奢&CB00264;&CB00264;胡摩兜<note place="inline">二</note>阿&CB00145;羯卑胡摩
<lb n="0885a04" ed="T"/>兜<note place="inline">三</note>破波羅胡摩兜<note place="inline">四</note>莎呵<note place="inline">五</note>。</p>
<lb n="0885a05" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0885a0501">&CB00057;水七遍與病人飲之。</p>
<lb n="0885a06" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0885a0601">腰&CB00560;痛鬼名</p>
<lb n="0885a07" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0885a0701">呼盧兜<note place="inline">一</note>波吒羅呼盧兜<note place="inline">二</note>毘<note n="0885002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">魔＝摩【明】</note><app n="0885002"><lem wit="【大】">魔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">摩</rdg></app>羅呼盧兜<note place="inline">三</note>
<lb n="0885a08" ed="T"/>彌梨耆梨卑呼盧兜<note place="inline">四</note>莎呵<note place="inline">五</note>。</p>
<lb n="0885a09" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0885a0901">&CB00057;三色縷青黃綠。結作七結。繫&CB00560;腕次繫髀
<lb n="0885a10" ed="T"/>後繫腰。</p>
<lb n="0885a11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0885a1101">頭痛鬼名</p>
<lb n="0885a12" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0885a1201">胡摩兜摩呵迦吒羅<note place="inline">一</note>毘摩迦吒羅<note place="inline">二</note>呼呼羅
<lb n="0885a13" ed="T"/>迦吒羅<note place="inline">三</note>伊呼迦吒羅<note place="inline">四</note>伊<note n="0885003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">未＝末【三】</note><note n="0885003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">未＝末【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0885003"><lem wit="【大】">未</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">末</rdg></app>迦知迦吒羅<note place="inline">五</note>
<lb n="0885a14" ed="T"/>莎呵<note place="inline">六</note>。</p>
<lb n="0885a15" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0885a1501">七遍&CB00057;楊枝打二七下。</p>
<lb n="0885a16" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0885a1601">闇鈍鬼名</p>
<lb n="0885a17" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0885a1701"><note n="0885004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB01654;＝呼【三】</note><note n="0885004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB01654;＝呼【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0885004"><lem wit="【大】">&CB01654;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">呼</rdg></app>吒吒<note place="inline">一</note>浮律置浮吒吒<note place="inline">二</note>阿支拏呼吒吒<note place="inline">三</note>
<lb n="0885a18" ed="T"/>浮律置支呼吒吒<note place="inline">四</note>伊呼破羅支呼吒吒<note place="inline">五</note>私
<lb n="0885a19" ed="T"/>蜜兜伊呼支破羅<note place="inline">六</note>莎呵<note n="0885005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔七〕－【宋】</note><app n="0885005"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">七</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">&lac;</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0885a20" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0885a2001">三七遍&CB00057;七日日三遍。</p>
<lb n="0885a21" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0885a2101">耳痛鬼名</p>
<lb n="0885a22" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0885a2201">比膩波<note place="inline">一</note>阿制置毘膩波<note place="inline">二</note>呼膩置毘膩波<note place="inline">三</note>
<lb n="0885a23" ed="T"/>伊呼支膩<note n="0885006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">置＋（毘）【元】【明】</note><app n="0885006"><lem wit="【大】">置</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">置毘</rdg></app>膩波<note place="inline">四</note>耆摩膩<note n="0885007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（置）＋毘【元】【明】</note><app n="0885007"><lem wit="【大】">毘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">置毘</rdg></app>膩波<note place="inline">五</note>莎呵
<lb n="0885a24" ed="T"/><note n="0885008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔六〕－【宋】</note><app n="0885008"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">六</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">&lac;</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0885a25" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0885a2501">於月生一日。設使左耳痛南向坐。右耳痛北
<lb n="0885a26" ed="T"/>向<note n="0885009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔坐〕－【宋】</note><app n="0885009"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">&lac;</rdg></app>。東向門病人門內坐&CB00057;師門外坐。水亦
<lb n="0885a27" ed="T"/>門<note n="0885010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">外＋（&CB00057;）【三】</note><note n="0885010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">外＋（&CB00057;）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0885010"><lem wit="【大】">外</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">外&CB00057;</rdg></app>二七遍三&CB01834;之。</p>
<lb n="0885a28" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0885a2801">淋鬼名</p>
<lb n="0885a29" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0885a2901">破波羅<note place="inline">一</note>浮梨浮梨置破波羅<note place="inline">二</note>車<note n="0885011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">慕＝暮【三】</note><note n="0885011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慕＝暮【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0885011"><lem wit="【大】">慕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">暮</rdg></app>那破波
<pb n="0885b" id="T21.1367.0885b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0885b01" ed="T"/>羅<note place="inline">三</note>呼呼羅車波羅<note place="inline">四</note>。</p>
<lb n="0885b02" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0885b0201">熱病鬼神病。方道蠱毒&CB00057;術。毘多<app source="0884015" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">茶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">荼</rdg></app>富多
<lb n="0885b03" ed="T"/>那等。善男子善女人所至之處。若行道中若
<lb n="0885b04" ed="T"/>水道中若急難處應念此&CB00057;。無有夜叉復多
<lb n="0885b05" ed="T"/>毘舍遮拘槃<app source="0884015" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">茶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">荼</rdg></app>迦<note n="0885012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">吒＝&CB00062;【三】</note><note n="0885012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吒＝&CB00062;【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0885012"><lem wit="【大】">吒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&CB00062;</rdg></app>富多那羅剎毘多<app source="0884015" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">茶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">荼</rdg></app>
<lb n="0885b06" ed="T"/>等畏。又無水火刀杖兵凶毒藥衰害&CB00057;術方
<lb n="0885b07" ed="T"/>道一切諸惡人非人等如是諸畏。阿難若有
<lb n="0885b08" ed="T"/>恐怖急難。應誦念此&CB00057;。無能作衰惱者。復次
<lb n="0885b09" ed="T"/>阿難若有受持讀誦此&CB00057;。如上天龍鬼神二
<lb n="0885b10" ed="T"/>十八部人非人等。不能越犯此&CB00057;。鐵輪金剛
<lb n="0885b11" ed="T"/>輪當為作苦患。令頭破作七分。四方四維上
<lb n="0885b12" ed="T"/>下若。有於此人起惡心者。悉皆繫其毒心令
<lb n="0885b13" ed="T"/>不發起。是善男子善女人。應善讀誦執持奉
<lb n="0885b14" ed="T"/>行。</p>
<lb n="0885b15" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>佛說大普賢陀羅尼經</jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>